Package ch.ecma.csta.system

Not supported.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SystemListener
    Initiates an event on a previous System Registration for change in the status of Tlink(s).
    SystemServices
    A set of services that allow an application to query and receive events on the status of Tlink connection(s) to the switch(es).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SystemAdapter
    Provides a callback method for each system service event type.

Package ch.ecma.csta.system Description

Not supported. In the future, this package will provide the classes for registering the computing function for system services. CSTA System Services are specified in ECMA-269, section 14.

In the meantime, use the TerminalServices class provided by Avaya to gain exclusive control over Communication Manager stations.
